edu.harvard.cga.gtools.tekml
Class KmlTimeSource

java.lang.Object
  edu.harvard.cga.gtools.tekml.KmlTimeSource
Direct Known Subclasses:
AttributeTableTimeSource, FixedKmlTimeSource
public abstract class KmlTimeSource
extends java.lang.Object

Implementations will, as delegates of a KmlRewriter, provide the time/date data object to the rewriter. This is made as general as possible given the non-standard ways this might be implemented in various KML providers, such as with attribute tables embedded as CDATA sections in the element. It also enables other external methods.

Author:
W.Hays (whays at nearity.com)
